Variable is a container which holds a value

DataType VariableName = Vaule;

Naming convections:-
1.Legal identifiers and may contains unicode letteres and digits.
2.Variable name can be starts from $,_ and letter
3.Can't be java reservered keyword
4.CamelCase
5.For Constant Varible should be in CAPTIAL LETTERS

Type of varaible:-
1.Primitive
2.References

1.Primitive types are of 8 types:-
a.char
b.byte
c.short
d.int
f.long
g.float
h.doulbe
i.boolean